{
  "stem": "12904.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so he did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I have a picture of that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then, he was promoted, which  he should have been to begin with.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Anyway, he was there until the end of the war, on November 18.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They told me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Naturally, I did not know him when he came back.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was only two years old and apparently did not recognize him as my father, wouldn't go to him, initially.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But anyway, we-- he had a thriving practice, a law practice.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Build it up again after the war and had two secretaries, as I recall.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He was by himself.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we bought a house.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We lived in an apartment and then bought a house in 1927, which my father told us he bought with the money he saved from giving up smoking.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because he didn't want us to start smoking.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So anyway, we went to-- the school system is different in Germany as it is in the United States.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "High school starts in the fifth grade.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I was allowed to skip the fourth grade and go directly from grade school to high school, the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was named after a queen, whom I-- I don't remember when she lived, I think in the 19th century some time.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And it was a gymnasium, which means it was led all the way to the end exam which is the abitur, A-B-I-T-U-R, or maturum.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I had to take two street cars to go there at the age of nine, but I managed.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Seemed to manage pretty well.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was-- we had a lot of culture in the house.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had evenings, music evenings.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I learned to play the violin from the time I was about eight years old.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Both my parents played piano.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
